ABOUT GTA SAN ANDREAS

Five years ago Carl Johnson escaped from the pressures of life in Los Santos. Now, it's the early 90s. On his return to the neighborhood, a couple of corrupt cops frame him for homicide. CJ is forced on a journey that takes him across the entire state of San Andreas.
